<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>About | BCA Examiner Allotment</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/styles.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/about.css">
    <script src="/js/scripts.js"></script>
</head>
<body>

    <%- include('partials/header') %>

    <!-- Hero Section -->
    <section class="hero">
        <div class="hero-content">
            <h1>About the Examiner Allotment System</h1>
            <p>Streamlining the allocation of external examiners for BCA practical exams to ensure **fairness, transparency, and efficiency**.</p>
        </div>
    </section>

    <!-- About Section -->
    <section class="about">
        <div class="container">
            <div class="about-content">
                <h2>Why This System?</h2>
                <p>The traditional method of assigning external examiners manually often led to **inefficiencies, bias, and logistical challenges**. This system is designed to eliminate those issues by providing an **automated, transparent, and data-driven** solution.</p>
            </div>

            <div class="about-grid">
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>🔄 Automated Allocation</h3>
                    <p>Examiners are assigned based on **location, availability, and expertise**, ensuring optimal resource distribution.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>📊 Performance Tracking</h3>
                    <p>Monitor **examiner efficiency, visit records, and compliance** through a dedicated dashboard.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>📍 Location-Based Assignments</h3>
                    <p>Reduces **travel time and logistical challenges** by prioritizing examiners closer to assigned colleges.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="about-card">
                    <h3>✅ Fair & Transparent</h3>
                    <p>Ensures **equal distribution of responsibilities**, preventing examiner overload and favoritism.</p>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="about-footer">
                <h2>Key Benefits</h2>
                <ul>
                    <li>✔️ Reduced administrative workload</li>
                    <li>✔️ Increased efficiency in examiner assignments</li>
                    <li>✔️ Improved compliance and record-keeping</li>
                    <li>✔️ Enhanced fairness and transparency</li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>

    <%- include('partials/footer') %>

</body>
</html>
